headline: Paychex Announces $1 Billion Stock Repurchase Authorization and Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., January 16, 2026--Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX), an industry-leading human capital management ("HCM") company, today announced that its Board of Directors has authorized the purchase of up to $1 billion of the Company’s common stock. The new authorization replaces the prior 2024 authorization to repurchase $400 million of the Company’s common stock.
